#Anorexianervosa occurs most commonly in adolescent girls from affluent families with perfectionist personalities.
#Anorexianervosa risk factors include participation in activities w/ pressure to be slim (eg, gymnastics, ballet, beauty pageants).
Individuals w/ #anorexianervosa may fast and hyper-exercise or purge with laxatives or vomiting (binging/purging subtype)
#AnorexiaNervosa, On physical examination, the most striking finding is emaciation.
#AnorexiaNervosa. Other common findings include bradycardia, hypotension, hypothermia, hair loss, and dry skin.
